                     <interp inst="t17880402-40-off200" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17880402-40-cd201" type="crimeDate">18th day of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880402-40-off200 t17880402-40-cd201"></join> last, a live boar pig, value 4 l. three live sow-pigs, value 8 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17880402-40-victim435" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Alsop
                  <interp inst="t17880402-40-victim435" type="surname" value="Alsop"></interp>
